"content": "<h2>Gall is a bitter herb</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:3-Prov5:4\">PRO 5:3–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:19-Ps69:21\">PSA 69:19–69:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:13-Lam3:15\">LAM 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:19-Lam3:20\">LAM 3:19–3:20</a></p>\n<h2>Gall was offered to Jesus Christ at the crucifixion</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:33-Matt27:34\">MAT 27:33–27:34</a></p>\n<h2>Gall is a secretion of the liver</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:12-Job16:13\">JOB 16:12–16:13</a></strong></p>",
